            <div className="mt-3 p-2 bg-blue-100 rounded text-xs">
              <strong>Important:</strong> Product weight à¤•à¥‹ Product Prices sheet à¤®à¥‡à¤‚ define à¤•à¤°à¤¨à¤¾ à¤œà¤°à¥‚à¤°à¥€ à¤¹à¥ˆ. à¤«à¤¿à¤° system automatically à¤‰à¤¸ weight à¤•à¥‡ basis à¤ªà¤° correct shipping rate apply à¤•à¤°à¥‡à¤—à¤¾.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
